            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#TA #AA">
                <p>Publius Alfesius Salvus, son of Publius, farewell! He lived nineteen years.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" resp="#AA">
                <p>Whilst the nomen Alfesius is unique, Salvus (or Salvius) is extremely common among freedpersons and enslaves persons.</p>
            </div>
